subtitleNullable: Digimon introduced between January 2020 and September 2023
descriptionNullable:
This dataset contains 1 image of every Digimon introduced between January 1, 2020 and September 19, 2023. The sole exception is 1 newly introduced Digimon that did not have an image by this point. All images come from the corresponding page on [Wikimon.net](wikimon.net).

To make your own dataset of Digimon from a certain range of years, use [this page](https://wikimon.net/Category:Digimon_by_year_of_introduction).
